race.comment: CARPACCIO (11) returned in good order with a solid win at Ipswich before just running into one better at the Sunny Coast last time out. Gets in well at the weights with the 2kg claim and should be right there when the whips are cracking. MIDNIGHT SPIRIT (12) has been just behind the placegetters at the past couple of outings and again gets the deadly Gollan/Maloney combination. Should prove tough to rein in. MORE TROUBLE (9) has won over this mile journey and maps ideally for this from gate two. Has to be included in calculations. SPECIAL ARTIST (15) got the job done here at the latest effort and looks ready for the step-up to the mile journey now. In the mix. DIAMOND EPIC (13) has only missed the top-five once in 11 career outings and will run her usual honest race.
